welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Honeygo, a charming city known for its beautiful parks and friendly locals. We hope you enjoy your stay and take some time to explore all that our city has to offer!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Concourse B

terminals.name: Concourse C

terminals.name: Main Terminal
